data.eml:eml: A review of world Diallactiini (Diptera, Cecidomyiidae, Winnertziinae), with the description of six new genera and seventeen new species

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Jaschhof, Mathias (2016): A review of world Diallactiini (Diptera, Cecidomyiidae, Winnertziinae), with the description of six new genera and seventeen new species. Zootaxa 4127 (2): 201-244, DOI: http://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4127.2.1
